name: Repealed ARTICLE 17. INSURANCE INFORMATION PROTECTION ACT--REPEALED
text:
§431:16-219  REPEALED.  L 2012, c 250, §13.
 
Note
 
  The 2012 repeal of this section shall not apply to any proceedings in which a member insurer is placed under an order of liquidation prior to July 1, 2012.  L 2012, c 250, §15.
